<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MIN SUNG CH106</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh min kha vaa lak hmanh u, Ngaihchia milung rethei hna, Nangmah
 hnangamnak an pek lai, Na kalnak kip ah keng tuah.

[C1]
   Maw sung bik, dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak, Maw sungbik,
   dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak.

[V2]
 Thinphannak vialte an phenh ca, Jesuh min i ken zungzal, Tukforhnak
 nih an naih tikah, Amah min khan thlacam tuah.

[C2]
   Maw sung bik, dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak, Maw sungbik,
   dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak.

[V3]
 Maw Jesuh a min sung bik kha, Kan thlarau a lawmhter ca'h, A kut in a
 kan pom tikah, Amah kha hla kan phuah lai.

[C3]
   Maw sung bik, dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak, Maw sungbik,
   dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak.

[V4]
 Bawi Jesuh min kan theih tikah, Amah hmaiah kan kun lai, Vancung khua
 ah kan tlun tikah, &quot;Bawi bik a si,&quot; kan ti lai.

[C4]
   Maw sung bik, dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak, Maw sungbik,
   dawtnak min, Vancung le vawlei lawmhnak.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>106</hymn_number>
</song>